						<summary>

						<p>Slab built in to the platform, near the shrine of Rāma.</p>						

						<p>This is dated in the cyclic year <hi rend="bold">Nandana, Vaiśakha ba. 5, Sunday.</hi></p>						

						<p>It registers the endownment of a trough <hi rend="italic">(gāḍi)</hi> at Penikalapāḍu by the six sons (names are given) of Tippireḍḍi of Nandavaram, for the merit of their parents. In characters of 17th century A.D.</p>						

						</summary>
